  • .
In [ ]:
select 
    oi.item_id,
    i.product_name,
    sum(sales) as 
from order_info oi left join item i 
on oi.item_id = i.item_id
group by oi.item_id, i.product_name
order by  desc;

05. 월별 상품 매출 분석(시계열 분석)¶

In [ ]:
select 
    SUBSTR(RESERV_NO,1,6) ,
    sum(DECODE(item_id, 'M0001', sales, 0)) special_set,
    sum(DECODE(item_id, 'M0002', sales, 0)) pasta,
    sum(DECODE(item_id, 'M0003', sales, 0)) pizza,
    sum(DECODE(item_id, 'M0004', sales, 0)) sea_food,
    sum(DECODE(item_id, 'M0005', sales, 0)) steak,
    sum(DECODE(item_id, 'M0006', sales, 0)) salad_bar,
    sum(DECODE(item_id, 'M0007', sales, 0)) salad,
    sum(DECODE(item_id, 'M0008', sales, 0)) sandwitch,
    sum(DECODE(item_id, 'M0009', sales, 0)) wine,
    sum(DECODE(item_id, 'M0010', sales, 0)) juice
from order_info
group by SUBSTR(RESERV_NO,1,6) 
order by ;

08. 예약 완료/취소건 분석¶

In [ ]:
select 
    substr(RESERV_DATE,1,6) ,
    sum(sales) - sum(decode(item_id, 'M0001', sales, 0)) etc,
    sum(decode(item_id, 'M0001', sales, 0)) special_set,
    round(sum(decode(item_id, 'M0001', sales, 0)) / sum(sales) * 100,1) ,
    count(*) ,
    sum(decode(cancel, 'N', 1,0)) ,
    sum(decode(cancel, 'Y', 1,0)) 
from reservation r left join order_info o 
on r.RESERV_NO = o.RESERV_NO
group by substr(RESERV_DATE,1,6)
order by ;

09. 월별 취소율 추이 분석¶

select 
    substr(RESERV_DATE,1,6) ,
    count(*) ,
    sum(decode(cancel, 'N', 1,0)) ,
    sum(decode(cancel, 'Y', 1,0)) ,
    round((sum(decode(cancel, 'Y', 1,0)) / count(*))*100,1) || '%'  
from reservation r left join order_info o 
on r.RESERV_NO = o.RESERV_NO
group by substr(RESERV_DATE,1,6)
order by ;

10. 요일별 매출 분석¶

In [ ]:
select 
    substr(reserv_date,1,6) ,
    'SPECIAL_SET' ,
    sum(decode(to_char(to_date(r.reserv_date),'day'), '', sales, 0)) , 
    sum(decode(to_char(to_date(r.reserv_date),'day'), '', sales, 0)) ,
    sum(decode(to_char(to_date(r.reserv_date),'day'), '', sales, 0)) ,
    sum(decode(to_char(to_date(r.reserv_date),'day'), '', sales, 0)) ,
    sum(decode(to_char(to_date(r.reserv_date),'day'), '', sales, 0)) ,
    sum(decode(to_char(to_date(r.reserv_date),'day'), '', sales, 0)) ,
    sum(decode(to_char(to_date(r.reserv_date),'day'), '', sales, 0)) 
from reservation r  join order_info o on r.reserv_no = o.reserv_no 
join item i on o.item_id = i.item_id
where i.item_id = 'M0001'
group by substr(reserv_date,1,6)
order by ;

11. 월별 전용 상품 실적 순위 분석¶

  • 1~3
In [ ]:
select * from 
(select 
    substr(reserv_date,1,6) 
    , branch 
    , sum(sales) 
    , rank() over(partition by substr(reserv_date,1,6) 
        order by sum(sales) desc) 
from reservation r join order_info o
on r.reserv_no = o.reserv_no
where o.item_id = 'M0001'
group by substr(reserv_date,1,6), branch
order by ,  desc)
where  = 1;

13. 개인별 매출 분석¶

select 
    c.customer_id 
    , c.customer_name 
    , count(o.sales) 
    , sum(o.sales) 
    , count(DECODE(o.item_id, 'M0001', sales, 0)) 
    , sum(DECODE(o.item_id, 'M0001', sales, 0))  
from customer c join reservation r on c.customer_id = r.customer_id
join order_info o on o.reserv_no = r.reserv_no
group by c.customer_id, c.customer_name
order by  desc;

14. 상위 매출 기준 10위 고객¶

  • 10 (row_number)
In [ ]:
select * from
(select 
    c.customer_id 
    , c.customer_name 
    , sum(DECODE(o.item_id, 'M0001', sales, 0))  
    , row_number() over (order by sum(DECODE(o.item_id, 'M0001', sales, 0)) desc) 
from customer c join reservation r on c.customer_id = r.customer_id
join order_info o on o.reserv_no = r.reserv_no  
group by c.customer_id, c.customer_name)
where  <= 10;
